Class AOfRhoAndZLoader

Namespace
Vts.MonteCarlo.Sources
Assembly
Vts.dll

class to handle loading of absorbed energy results from prior simulation. Because our code tallies photon contributions beyond the final grid bin, into the final grid bin, the final grid bins are excluded from the fluorescent source.
